<demos>
   <name>DirectSD Control</name>
   <type>toolbox</type>
   <icon>$toolbox/matlab/icons/matlabicon.gif</icon>
   <description><![CDATA[
<p>The DirectSD Toolbox is a collection of 
M-files for direct analysis and design of     
sampled-data control systems.        
The Toolbox contains functions to perform
both frequency-domain and state-space analysis
and design of sampled-data systems with generalized
holds with account for their continuous-time 
behaviour.  Using the DirectSD Toolbox, you can also
design reduced-order quasioptimal controllers by
means of global search algorithms.
</p>
]]></description>


